I'd like to be able to tell sleep to sleep `forever'.  This would be
useful in combination with the flock(1l) program I sent in a few days
ago.

I also suggest that sleep identify itself before the error message
	bad character

something like:
	sleep: bad character
or
	sleep: usage [seconds]

